Sentencas: Strontium and nickel co-doped layerd-perovskite PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2-xNixO5+delta (PBSCN) with various proportions of nickel (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3, abbreviated as PBSCN-1, PBSCN-2 and PBSCN-3, respectively) are investigated as cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The PBSCN powders are synthesized by a combined EDTA-citrate complexing sol-gel method.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Then PBSCN pellets are sintered at 1100 degrees C for 10 h in air.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The materials exhibit an orthorhombic structure with the space group of Pmmm.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity is determined by the van der Pauw method at the temperature range of 400-800 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: It is shown that the electrical conductivity declines with increasing temperature for all the samples.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The highest conductivity of 1590 S cm(-1) for PBSCN-3 is obtained at 400 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) decreases with the increase of Ni content.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The average TEC at the temperature range of 30-900 degrees C decreases from 21.9 x 10(-6) K-1 for PBSCN-1 to 19.7 x 10(-6) K-1 for PBSCN-3.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) with thickness in 0.3 mm is used as the electrolyte in this study.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Electrolyte supported fuel cells prepared by coating method are employed to study the electrochemical properties from 600 to 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The polarization resistances of PBSCN samples on YSZ electrolyte at 800 degrees C are 0.297, 0.314 and 0.321 Omega cm(2) for PBSCN-1, PBSCN-2 and PBSCN-3, respectively.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The single fuel cell with the configuration of PBSCN-1/YSZ/Pt delivers the highest power density of 120 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C. (C) 2014
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xNixO5+δ (x=0.1, 0.2 and 0.3) cathodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs
